{"tid":1753514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環球時報總編 : 西方勢力為港反對派助選，「香港的天永遠都是中国的天，香港的地永遠都是中国的地」","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T03:38:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f8b15bb766a583fba5828383c5b0b2fbafb71f","tid":1753514,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/11/25/2311688_ed6881e537a8204997f8a91cbeecaf05_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F11%2F25%2F2311688_ed6881e537a8204997f8a91cbeecaf05_320.jpg&h=a923a3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地官媒《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進在微博發文，批評西方一些勢力，在香港區議會選舉中拼命為反對派助選，包括叛逃中國特工自爆在香港搞滲透、英國駐港總領事館前僱員受訪，以及美國參眾兩院短時間通過《香港人權與民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進認為，無論哪一方獲得更多席位，區議會能夠被政治化的空間都有限，強調「香港的天永遠都是中國的天，香港的地永遠都是中國的地，香港處在中國的治下，這個事實永遠變不了。」<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2311688/%E3%80%90%E5%8D%80%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E8%83%A1%E9%8C%AB%E9%80%B2%3A%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%8B%A2%E5%8A%9B%E7%82%BA%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE%E5%8A%A9%E9%81%B8</code></pre>"},{"pid":"6998d2d6d89aa7087253b198fe74b393711f9ae0","tid":1753514,"uid":268243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:20:57.000Z","msg":"香港的人永遠都是香港人"},{"pid":"0549abfb827ff432ab8be61315c09dc224c34932","tid":1753514,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9c64fbc85ba2159094ff617fb5f231aa4e21f6","tid":1753514,"uid":247471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"香港人永遠只係香港人，強國人永遠唔係香港人"}]}